{
  "texts": [
    "where A geom is the geometrical area of the antenna dish in units of m 2, and k = 1.38 × 10 3 is the Boltzmann constant in units of Jy m 2 /K.",
    "A summary of the station DPFUs and gain curve parameters for the EHT array in 2018 is provided in Table A.1, together with their estimated uncertainties.",
    "Details on their derivation for each station are described by Koay et al. (2023a).",
    "We expect the DPFU uncertainties to be the dominant source of systematic errors in the flux density calibration of EHT data.",
    "T * sys values are not expected to vary much within the typical scan duration of a few minutes, so their uncertainties are expected to be no larger than a few percent."
  ]
}